  <entry>
    <title>Leetcode Hot 100 题解04</title>
    <url>/2021/03/01/Leetcode-Hot-100-%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A304/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2 id="题目：-寻找两个正序数组的中位数（中等）"><a href="#题目：-寻找两个正序数组的中位数（中等）" class="headerlink" title="题目： 寻找两个正序数组的中位数（中等）"></a>题目： 寻找两个正序数组的中位数（中等）</h2><p>给定两个大小分别为 m 和 n 的正序（从小到大）数组 nums1 和 nums2。请你找出并返回这两个正序数组的 中位数 。</p>
<h3 id="示例"><a href="#示例" class="headerlink" title="示例"></a>示例</h3><p><strong>输入：</strong> nums1 = [1,3], nums2 = [2]</p>
<p><strong>输出：</strong> 2.00000</p>
<p><strong>解释</strong> 合并数组 = [1,2,3] ，中位数 2</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2 id="解题思路"><a href="#解题思路" class="headerlink" title="解题思路"></a>解题思路</h2><p>因为两个数组都是排序完毕的，因此我们可以采用归并的思想合并两个数组，然后计算合并后数组的中位数。</p>
<p>进阶思路： 使用二分法可以将时间复杂度变为O（log(m+n)）, 详细题解见leetcode。</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2 id="题解代码"><a href="#题解代码" class="headerlink" title="题解代码"></a>题解代码</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Solution</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">findMedianSortedArrays</span>(<span class="params">self, nums1: List[<span class="built_in">int</span>], nums2: List[<span class="built_in">int</span>]</span>) -&gt; float:</span></span><br><span class="line">        res = []</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> nums1 <span class="keyword">and</span> nums2:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> nums1[<span class="number">0</span>] &lt;= nums2[<span class="number">0</span>]:</span><br><span class="line">                res.append(nums1.pop(<span class="number">0</span>))</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                res.append(nums2.pop(<span class="number">0</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        res += nums1 <span class="keyword">or</span> nums2</span><br><span class="line">        length = <span class="built_in">len</span>(res)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> length%<span class="number">2</span> == <span class="number">1</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> res[length//<span class="number">2</span>]</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> (res[length//<span class="number">2</span>-<span class="number">1</span>] + res[length//<span class="number">2</span>])/<span class="number">2</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>算法</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Leetcode</tag>
      </tags>
