  <entry>
    <title>Leetcode Hot 100 题解05</title>
    <url>/2021/03/01/Leetcode-Hot-100-%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A305/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2 id="题目：-最长回文子串（中等）"><a href="#题目：-最长回文子串（中等）" class="headerlink" title="题目： 最长回文子串（中等）"></a>题目： 最长回文子串（中等）</h2><p>给你一个字符串 s，找到 s 中最长的回文子串。</p>
<h3 id="示例"><a href="#示例" class="headerlink" title="示例"></a>示例</h3><p><strong>输入：</strong> s = “babad”</p>
<p><strong>输出：</strong> “bab”</p>
<p><strong>解释</strong> “aba” 同样是符合题意的答案。</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2 id="解题思路"><a href="#解题思路" class="headerlink" title="解题思路"></a>解题思路</h2><p>典型的动态规划问题，遇到这类求最长的字符串肿的子串，一般思路就是二维dp。<br>我们定义dp[i][j]为字符串从i开始一直到j（包括j）的子串的最长回文长度。如果子串不是回文子串，赋值为0。</p>
<p>如果我们知道子串开始与结尾两个字符相同，那么只需要判断他们之间是否为回文子串，若是则长度加2，若不是则长度为0。假如开始与结尾两个字符串不同，则直接可以判断长度为0.</p>
<p>状态转移方程为：<br>dp[i][j] = dp[i+1][j-1] + 2 if s[i] == s[j] &amp; dp[i+1][j-1] != 0</p>
<p>这里的另一个关键是如何初始化与如何全部遍历完成。首先我们易得dp[i][i] = 1，即初始化所有长度为1的子串。接下来考虑如果我们要得到dp[0][1], 显然不能使用转移方程，因为这样的子串只有两个字符，去掉开头结尾后变为空，在dp数组中不存在。因此我们还要初始化所有长度为2的子串。对于长度大于等于3的子串，我们才可以使用状态转移方程。<br>&nbsp;</p>
<h2 id="题解代码"><a href="#题解代码" class="headerlink" title="题解代码"></a>题解代码</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Solution</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">longestPalindrome</span>(<span class="params">self, s: <span class="built_in">str</span></span>) -&gt; str:</span></span><br><span class="line">        length = <span class="built_in">len</span>(s)</span><br><span class="line">        dp = [[<span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">for</span> _ <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(length)] <span class="keyword">for</span> _ <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(length)]</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 初始化长度为1的子串</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(length):</span><br><span class="line">            dp[i][i] = <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            res = s[<span class="number">0</span>]</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 初始化长度为2的子串</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(length-<span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> s[i] == s[i+<span class="number">1</span>]:</span><br><span class="line">                dp[i][i+<span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">                res = s[i:i+<span class="number">2</span>]</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 开始计算长度从3开始的子串一直到length-1</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> j <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">2</span>, length):</span><br><span class="line">            i = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">while</span> i+j &lt; length:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> s[i] == s[i+j]:</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">if</span> dp[i+<span class="number">1</span>][i+j-<span class="number">1</span>] != <span class="number">0</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                        dp[i][i+j] = dp[i+<span class="number">1</span>][i+j-<span class="number">1</span>]+<span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">if</span> dp[i][i+j] &gt; <span class="built_in">len</span>(res):</span><br><span class="line">                            res = s[i:i+j+<span class="number">1</span>]</span><br><span class="line">                i += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> res</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>算法</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Leetcode</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>Leetcode Hot 100 题解06</title>
    <url>/2021/03/02/Leetcode-Hot-100-%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A306/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2 id="题目：-正则表达式匹配（困难）"><a href="#题目：-正则表达式匹配（困难）" class="headerlink" title="题目： 正则表达式匹配（困难）"></a>题目： 正则表达式匹配（困难）</h2><p>给你一个字符串 s 和一个字符规律 p，请你来实现一个支持 &#39;.&#39; 和 &#39;*&#39; 的正则表达式匹配。</p>
<p>‘.’ 匹配任意单个字符<br>‘*’ 匹配零个或多个前面的那一个元素<br>所谓匹配，是要涵盖 整个 字符串 s的，而不是部分字符串。</p>
<p>注：</p>
<p>s 可能为空，且只包含从 a-z 的小写字母。<br>p 可能为空，且只包含从 a-z 的小写字母，以及字符 . 和 *。<br>保证每次出现字符 * 时，前面都匹配到有效的字符</p>
<h3 id="示例1"><a href="#示例1" class="headerlink" title="示例1"></a>示例1</h3><p><strong>输入：</strong> s = “aa” p = “a”</p>
<p><strong>输出：</strong> false</p>
<p><strong>解释</strong> “a” 无法匹配 “aa” 整个字符串。</p>
<h3 id="示例2"><a href="#示例2" class="headerlink" title="示例2"></a>示例2</h3><p><strong>输入：</strong> s = “ab” p = “.*“</p>
<p><strong>输出：</strong> true</p>
<p><strong>解释</strong> “.*“ 表示可匹配零个或多个（’*‘）任意字符（’.’）。</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2 id="解题思路"><a href="#解题思路" class="headerlink" title="解题思路"></a>解题思路</h2><p>首先我们定义dp[i][j]为s前i个字符与p前j个字符是否匹配, 此时考虑s[:i], p[:j],因此最后一个字符的索引为i-1, j-1。那么显然我们可以初始化dp[0][0]=True，因为两个空字符串必然是匹配的。接下来继续考虑，当s为空字符串时，只有p的偶数位全为’*‘时，s与p才能匹配。因此，可以确定当i=0时，dp[0][j] = dp[0][j-2] 如果 p[j-1] = ‘*‘。</p>
<p>由于s[i-1]必为小写字母 p[j-1]可能为字母，可能为‘.’, 也可能为’*‘.因此我们对p[j-1]分情况讨论</p>
<ol>
<li>当p[j-1] ！= ‘*’<ol>
<li>如果p[j-1] = ‘.’, 它与s[i-1]必然匹配，所以dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j-1]。</li>
<li>如果p[j-1] != ‘.’, 只有当s[i-1] = p[j-1]情况下我们才要去看s的前i-1个与p的j-1个是否匹配，即dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j-1], 否则就是不匹配。</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>p[j-1] 为’*’<br>存在两种情况：<ol>
<li>如果它与前一个字符的作用是表示前面字符有0个，那么dp[i][j] = dp[i][j-2]</li>
<li>如果它与前面字符表示有一个或多个，那么这个作用成立的必要条件是s[i-1]与p[j-2]匹配, 否则他们的作用只能表示0个。那么在表示一个或多个作用成立条件下，我们可以写出dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j-2]</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
<p>那么换个角度，我们也可以将上面的两种情况根据s[i-1]与p[j-2]是否匹配这个条件讨论得到：<br>    1. 如果匹配， 它的作用可以是表示0个，或者表示一个或多个，即dp[i][j] = dp[i][j-2] or dp[i-1][j-2]<br>    2. 如果不=匹配，它的作用只能是表示0个，即dp[i][j] = dp[i][j-2]</p>
<p>总结如下</p>
<ol>
<li>p[j-1] != ‘*’<br> dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j-1] if (p[j-1] == ‘.’ or s[i-1] == p[j-1]) else False</li>
<li>p[j-1] == ‘*’:<br> dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j] or dp[i][j-2] if p[j-1] == ‘.’ or s[i-1]==p[j-2] else dp[i][j-2]<br>&nbsp;</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="题解代码"><a href="#题解代码" class="headerlink" title="题解代码"></a>题解代码</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Solution</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">isMatch</span>(<span class="params">self, s: <span class="built_in">str</span>, p: <span class="built_in">str</span></span>) -&gt; bool:</span></span><br><span class="line">        row, col = <span class="built_in">len</span>(s)+<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="built_in">len</span>(p)+<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">        dp = [[<span class="literal">False</span> <span class="keyword">for</span> _ <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(col)] <span class="keyword">for</span> _ <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(row)]</span><br><span class="line">        dp[<span class="number">0</span>][<span class="number">0</span>] = <span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> j <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">2</span>, col, <span class="number">2</span>):</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> p[j-<span class="number">1</span>] == <span class="string">&#x27;*&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                dp[<span class="number">0</span>][j] = dp[<span class="number">0</span>][j-<span class="number">2</span>]</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, row):</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> j <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, col):</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> p[j-<span class="number">1</span>] == <span class="string">&#x27;*&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">if</span> p[j-<span class="number">2</span>] == <span class="string">&#x27;.&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">or</span> p[j-<span class="number">2</span>] == s[i-<span class="number">1</span>]:</span><br><span class="line">                        dp[i][j] = dp[i][j-<span class="number">2</span>] <span class="keyword">or</span> dp[i-<span class="number">1</span>][j]</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                        dp[i][j] = dp[i][j-<span class="number">2</span>]</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">if</span> p[j-<span class="number">1</span>] == <span class="string">&#x27;.&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">or</span> s[i-<span class="number">1</span>] == p[j-<span class="number">1</span>]:</span><br><span class="line">                        dp[i][j] = dp[i-<span class="number">1</span>][j-<span class="number">1</span>]</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> dp[-<span class="number">1</span>][-<span class="number">1</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<hr>
]]></content>
